# Files with MDX syntax that Mintlify cannot parse.
# See https://github.com/bazel-contrib/bazel-docs/issues/226

# The following were broken under the old HTML→Go→awk pipeline but should now be
# fixed thanks to gen_mdx_reference_docs (docs2mdx.py) producing clean MDX directly.
# Commented out to re-enable them in the nav.
# rules/lib/repo/*.mdx
# rules/lib/globals/bzl.mdx
# rules/lib/globals/module.mdx
# reference/be/functions.mdx
# reference/be/platforms-and-toolchains.mdx
# reference/command-line-reference.mdx

# Reference docs with complex HTML or template syntax
# flag-cheatsheet: raw <html devsite> wrapper, not converted to MDX
reference/flag-cheatsheet.mdx
# test-encyclopedia: Devsite heading anchors {:#anchor} not valid MDX
reference/test-encyclopedia.mdx

# Query docs with {{ '<var>' }} template patterns
query/language.mdx
# Multi-line <p> inside <Accordion> causes: "Expected closing tag for `<p>` before end of paragraph"
query/quickstart.mdx

# Misc files with unresolvable MDX syntax
community/roadmaps-configurability.mdx
concepts/build-files.mdx
